profile_positions.description:
Leading Deloitte’s Consulting practice in Porto. Key responsibilities include:
- Adjust the firm’s positioning and service offering to serve a local market more heavily reliant on manufacturing companies and SMBs;
- Develop and execute account plans to serve tier 1 and 2 accounts;
- Set up a local talent base to serve clients with a relevant set of business and technology capabilities.

Deloitte Digital is a business unit dedicated to addressing clients’ end-to-end digital transformation challenges. Pedro served as the Strategy Director at the newly setup organization for all non-Financial Services sectors with the responsibility for:
- Localizing Deloitte Digital's offering and portfolio to the Portuguese market;
- Setting up and upskilling the digital strategy team;
- Going to market in combination with industry, account and technology leads.
